{
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"job 工作流详解：\n1. run 创建任务，AI 自动生成执行计划并迭代执行\n2. 每次迭代 AI 执行一个子任务，更新进度\n3. 当所有子任务完成或达到 max-iterations 时停止，生成 DONE.md\n4. 可随时用 status 查看进度，用 stop 强制终止\n\ninit、iter、exec 均为内部实现，用户统一通过 run 创建任务。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Job workflow explained:\n1. run creates task, AI auto-generates execution plan and iterates\n2. Each iteration AI executes one subtask, updates progress\n3. Stops when all subtasks complete or max-iterations reached, generates DONE.md\n4. Use status anytime to check progress, stop to force terminate\n\ninit, iter, and exec are internal implementations. Users create tasks through run.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"job-id 使用技巧：\n- 自定义 ID：`x agent run --job-id fix-bug-123 \"Fix login\"`\n- 跨命令追踪：`run --job-id mytask` → `status --job-id mytask` → `stop --job-id mytask`\n- 默认 ID：时间戳格式，如 260527_193035\n"
,
"en"
:
"Job-id usage tips:\n- Custom ID: `x agent run --job-id fix-bug-123 \"Fix login\"`\n- Cross-command tracking: `run --job-id mytask` → `status --job-id mytask` → `stop --job-id mytask`\n- Default ID: timestamp format, e.g. 260527_193035\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式选择：\n- 默认（tty）: 交互式表格，可点选操作\n- --tsv: 制表符分隔，适合命令行过滤 `x agent job ls --active | grep error`\n- --yml: YAML 结构化，适合 AI 解析和脚本处理\n- --csv: 逗号分隔，兼容 Excel 等工具\n"
,
"en"
:
"Output format choices:\n- Default (tty): Interactive table with selectable actions\n- --tsv: Tab-separated, good for CLI filtering `x agent job ls --active | grep error`\n- --yml: YAML structured, good for AI parsing and scripting\n- --csv: Comma-separated, compatible with Excel\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run \"Refactor authentication module\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 创建并执行任务，自动迭代直到完成"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Create and run task, auto-iterate until completion"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent run --job-id auth-fix --max-iterations 50 \"Fix OAuth\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定 job-id + 迭代上限，方便追踪"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Specified job-id + iteration limit, easy to track"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --yml --active"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: YAML 格式列出活跃任务（AI 可解析）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: YAML list of active tasks (AI-parseable)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job status --job-id auth-fix --yml"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看指定任务的完整状态（YAML，包含文件列表和运行状态）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View complete task status (YAML with file list and running state)"
}
]
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有任务，支持多种格式和过滤"
,
"en"
:
"List all tasks with multiple formats and filters"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent job ls [options]"
]
,
"--job-dir"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定任务父目录（默认 ~/.x-cmd/data/agent/job/）"
,
"en"
:
"Specify parent directory for jobs (default ~/.x-cmd/data/agent/job/)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
"--active"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"只显示活跃任务（有 PLAN.md 但无 DONE.md）"
,
"en"
:
"Show only active tasks (has PLAN.md but no DONE.md)"
}
}
,
"--completed"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"只显示已完成任务（有 DONE.md）"
,
"en"
:
"Show only completed tasks (has DONE.md)"
}
}
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"CSV 格式（适合导入 Excel）"
,
"en"
:
"CSV format (suitable for Excel import)"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"TSV 格式（默认非终端输出，适合管道处理）"
,
"en"
:
"TSV format (default for non-tty, good for piping)"
}
}
,
"--yml"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"YAML 格式（结构化，适合 AI 解析和脚本处理）"
,
"en"
:
"YAML format (structured, good for AI parsing and scripting)"
}
}
,
"--app"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"交互式应用模式（终端下默认，可点选查看/删除）"
,
"en"
:
"Interactive app mode (tty default, clickable view/delete)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 终端下进入交互选择，非终端输出 TSV"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Interactive select in terminal, TSV otherwise"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --active --yml"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: YAML 格式列出活跃任务（AI 可读）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: YAML list of active tasks (AI-readable)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --completed --csv > done.csv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: CSV 导出已完成任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: CSV export of completed tasks"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --job-dir ~/custom-jobs"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看自定义目录下的任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View tasks in custom directory"
}
]
}
,
"status"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看单个任务的详细状态（进度、迭代、文件、运行状态）。\ntty 下带颜色高亮，--yml 下输出纯结构化数据。\n"
,
"en"
:
"View detailed status of a single task (progress, iterations, files, running state).\nColored highlight in tty, pure structured data with --yml.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"status 输出字段说明：\n- job/jobdir: 任务 ID 和完整目录路径\n- status: 任务状态（active/completed/unknown）\n- running: 后台进程是否存活（通过 worker isalive 检测）\n- progress: 完成百分比和 TODO 进度\n- iteration: 当前迭代 / 最大迭代\n- ai: AI 状态、工作类型、退出信号、建议\n- stats: 修改文件数、测试状态、响应数\n- time: 创建和更新时间\n- core_files: 核心文件列表（AGENTS.md, PLAN.md 等）\n- response_files: 历次迭代的响应文件列表\n"
,
"en"
:
"Status output fields:\n- job/jobdir: Task ID and full directory path\n- status: Task state (active/completed/unknown)\n- running: Whether background process is alive (via worker isalive)\n- progress: Completion percentage and TODO progress\n- iteration: Current / maximum iterations\n- ai: AI status, work type, exit signal, recommendation\n- stats: Files modified, test status, response count\n- time: Creation and update timestamps\n- core_files: Core file list (AGENTS.md, PLAN.md, etc.)\n- response_files: Historical iteration response files\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent job status [options] [job_dir]"
]
,
"--job-dir"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定任务目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Specify task directory path"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
"--job-id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定任务 ID（最便捷，无需知道完整路径）"
,
"en"
:
"Specify job ID (most convenient, no need for full path)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"任务标识符"
,
"en"
:
"Job identifier"
}
}
}
,
"--yml"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"强制纯 YAML 输出（无颜色，结构化，适合 AI 解析）"
,
"en"
:
"Force pure YAML output (no colors, structured, AI-friendly)"
}
}
,
"--llms"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"LLM 优化输出（前置阅读指南 + YAML 数据 + 自动嵌入 DONE.md 内容）"
,
"en"
:
"LLM-optimized output (reading guide + YAML data + auto-embedded DONE.md)"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"任务目录路径（位置参数，与 --job-dir 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Task directory path (positional, alternative to --job-dir)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job status"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看最近任务的状态（彩色）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View most recent task status (colored)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job status --job-id mytask --yml"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定 job-id，YAML 格式输出（AI 可解析）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Specified job-id, YAML output (AI-parseable)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job status --job-dir ~/.x-cmd/data/agent/job/260527_193035"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 通过目录路径查看"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View by directory path"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job status --yml | x agent request --pipe \"Summarize this task\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 获取状态并通过 AI 总结"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get status and summarize via AI"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job status --llms"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: LLM 优化格式输出（含阅读指南和 DONE.md 内容）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: LLM-optimized format with reading guide and DONE.md content"
}
]
}
,
"run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用预定义 agent 配置运行任务，自动构建提示词并执行。"
,
"en"
:
"Run task using predefined agent config, auto-build prompt and execute."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent job run [options] <target> [arguments]"
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"快捷别名：`x agent run` 等同于 `x agent job run`\n完整参数和用例请参见 `x agent run --help`"
,
"en"
:
"Shortcut alias: `x agent run` is equivalent to `x agent job run`\nSee `x agent run --help` for full parameters and examples"
}
]
}
,
"stop"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停止指定任务的后台进程（任务状态会被保留）"
,
"en"
:
"Stop background process of specified task (task state is preserved)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent job stop [options]"
]
,
"--job-id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要停止的任务 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Job ID to stop"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"任务标识符"
,
"en"
:
"Job identifier"
}
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job stop --job-id job-260527_193035"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 停止指定任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop specified job"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job stop --job-id $(x agent ps | head -1)"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 停止第一个运行中的任务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop first running job"
}
]
}
}

